# Raw/large downloads land here; loaders fall back to synthetic if absent.
data/*
!data/README.md
# ...but DO ship the small preprocessed caches (e.g. afhq_32.npz, ~18 MB),
# built once by tools/prepare_data.py — students load these instantly.
!data/*.npz
# The right-sized capstone calo cache (12k showers, ~85 MB, under GitHub's 100 MB
# limit) ships committed too. The 50k master (_calochallenge_ds2_50k.hdf5) stays
# ignored — it's just the local source for re-skimming to another size.
!data/calochallenge_ds2.hdf5
# Large pre-trained models (distributed separately to the school).
checkpoints/*.pt
checkpoints/*.ckpt
# Notebook execution artifacts
.ipynb_checkpoints/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# Generated by cadence on the teacher's machine
*_registered.ipynb
*_student.ipynb
# Local-only maintainer notes (not shipped to students)
DEV_NOTES.md
